org.drip.state.identifier

Interface LatentStateLabel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollateralLabel, CreditLabel, CreditSupportAnnexLabel, CustomLabel, EquityLabel, FloaterLabel, ForwardLabel, FundingLabel, FXLabel, GovvieLabel, OTCFixFloatLabel, OvernightLabel, PaydownLabel, RatingLabel, RecoveryLabel, RepoLabel, VolatilityLabel

    public interface LatentStateLabel
    LatentStateLabel is the interface that contains the labels inside the sub-stretch of the alternate state. The functionality its derivations implement provide fully qualified label names and their matches.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
